fields.customfield_12850:
System shall create a Convenience Order for new or existing Orders (in the back end) if the following conditions are met:
Apply Convenience Fee based on Credit Card Payment Indicator is True for the Contract; and
There is at least one new payment being collected in the Shopping Cart belonging to the Credit Card
Payment group; and
All the Products in the Order in the Shopping Cart belong to product category and product sub category
that are configured for the associated Convenience Product.
System shall hide the newly created Convenience Order in the Shopping Cart as well as the Confirmation page.
Apply Convenience Fee.UCS
Process Cart.UCS
